{
  "stem": "2581.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So by the time we came to Dachau, we were both taken to the hospital.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And-- I remember, it had to be the very next day, that while I was myself they-- they kicked at this-- [INAUDIBLE] had given me had turned into a big [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] abscess, cyst with pus in it.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they had to operate on me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Was this after liberation?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, this were not doctors that did that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were called [INAUDIBLE], you know, not even paramedics.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "These were people that had learned those things from others in the camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And where I-- my injury was something that didn't need to-- you didn't have to be an expert.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You cut it open.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And if you healed, it healed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But my father, they amputated the left arm.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And within hours-- because it was all the same day, I remember saying Kaddish later-- this Italian, big guy, tall man, broad shoulders came over to me.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he said, [NON-ENGLISH], your comrade kaput.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Now, it wasn't my comrade.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was my father.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he saw that we came in together.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I remember like in a haze somebody saying Kaddish with me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And that was two days after liberation or three days.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I'm still confused which day we are liberated.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But I have a certificate of that that I have received from the-- the United Nations organization in Germany.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So I have the-- the date that my father died.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And it's two days after liberation.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And at that day, my whole world ended.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I-- I didn't want to go out from that hospital.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Because without my father, nothing else-- nothing else mattered.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
